      <title>印度小投资者上月向股票基金投入 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-small-investors-put-3-billion-in-stock-funds-last-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管近期出现抛售，印度散户投资者仍对当地股市保持信心，并向其每月投资计划投入了创纪录的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-small-investors-put-3-billion-in-stock-funds-last-month</guid>
